The OnboardingSection card is configured by default on the homepage for new devs as follows:

```yaml
dynamicPlugins:
  frontend:
    red-hat-developer-hub.backstage-plugin-dynamic-home-page:
      mountPoints:
        - mountPoint: home.page/cards
          importName: OnboardingSection
          config:
            layouts:
              xl: { w: 12, h: 6 }
              lg: { w: 12, h: 6 }
              md: { w: 12, h: 6 }
              sm: { w: 12, h: 6 }
              xs: { w: 12, h: 6 }
              xxs: { w: 12, h: 14.5 }
```

This configuration defines the layout and size of the OnboardingSection card on the homepage for new devs. The card is displayed with a width of 12 columns and a height of 6 units on extra-large screens, and its size adjusts accordingly on smaller screens.

