The specific requirement for the package_name key under dynamicPlugins.frontend is that it must match the value of scalprum.name in the plugin's package.json file. This ensures that the dynamic plugin loads correctly at runtime in Red Hat Developer Hub.

To achieve this, you can add the following to your package.json file before running the export command:

```json
{
  "publishConfig": {
    "registry": "<npm_registry_url>"
  }
}
```

